@Authy.Presentation_HostAddress = http://localhost:5238

### Create Organization (Platform Owner only)
POST {{Authy.Presentation_HostAddress}}/organizations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corporation",
  "allowSelfRegistration": true,
  "adminEmail": "admin@acme.com",
  "adminPassword": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### Get Organization
GET {{Authy.Presentation_HostAddress}}/organizations/{{orgId}}
Accept: application/json

### Create User in Organization
POST {{Authy.Presentation_HostAddress}}/organizations/{{orgId}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@acme.com",
  "password": "UserPassword123!",
  "role": "member"
}

### List Users in Organization
GET {{Authy.Presentation_HostAddress}}/organizations/{{orgId}}/users
Accept: application/json

### Get Specific User
GET {{Authy.Presentation_HostAddress}}/organizations/{{orgId}}/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json
